{"tid":50764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 梁天琦與記者被控打鬥案今日提堂","createTime":"2016-12-22T16:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T11:02:34.000Z","uid":47352,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2303f4a0fbe56ab761fda543850290d8b59634fa","tid":50764,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"本土民主前線成員梁天琦涉嫌在港鐵站內，與大公報記者的打架案，警方落案控告兩人在公眾地方打鬥，明天在東區法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，經調查及徵詢法律意見，分別落案控告二十五歲的梁天琦，和四十二歲盧姓男子，各一項在公眾地方打鬥罪。<br />\n<br />\n兩人星期五在東區法院提堂。案發在今年八月十三日，梁天琦與盧姓男子涉嫌在港鐵太古站內爭執和打鬥。<br />\n[url]梁天琦與記者被控打鬥案明提堂 <a href=\"http://m.i-cable.com/m-site/content_detail.php?id=114707[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.i-cable.com%2Fm-site%2Fcontent_detail.php%3Fid%3D114707%5B%2Furl%5D&d=2MnemgpOUhYQM1vUcZnwPQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=c3248e57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.i-cable.com/m-site/content_detail.php?id=114707[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"0be6d0d1891f95e795e7a4a02c41424b51bbd8b8","tid":50764,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71da258a277c4e465e02e8477ae390b135f43ed3","tid":50764,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06b8f15270a5edddbc98d42b738c69edf5a56a9","tid":50764,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"梁天琦只係俾人禁住黎打都俾人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b31402fa031f4dec3c1f6793f80c27f93e9322","tid":50764,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3415629aaf9d9bf0e42731a5455f776cf98b6cc","tid":50764,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"梁天崎就出人名，嗰條共